<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad">

<body>

<metal:leftportlets fill-slot="portlets_one">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-attendees" />
</metal:leftportlets>

<metal:rightportlets fill-slot="portlets_two">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-details" />
</metal:rightportlets>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">

  <div metal:use-macro="context/@@launchpad_form/form">

    <h1 metal:fill-slot="heading">Register your attendance</h1>

    <div metal:fill-slot="extra_info" class="documentDescription">
      Indicate the times during which you will be available for meetings at
      the sprint.  Use the sprint's local time.
    </div>

  </div>

</div>

<div metal:fill-slot="help">
<p>If you are attending the sprint, please register your attendance
dates.  This allows the sprint organisers to schedule the sessions to
maximise the number of sessions you can attend.</p>

<p>The times should be entered in the local time for the location of
the sprint, which is
<kbd tal:content="context/time_zone">UTC</kbd>.</p>
</div>
    
</body>
</html>

